# Base URL

```text
http://localhost:5000/api
```

---

# 1. Upload File to Local Storage

### Method

```http
POST
```

### URL

```text
http://localhost:5000/api/upload/local
```

### Body

Select

```
Body
    ↓
form-data
```

Key:

| Key  | Type | Value                          |
| ---- | ---- | ------------------------------ |
| file | File | Select an image/video/document |

Example:

```
file : photo.jpg
```

### Expected Response

```json
{
    "_id": "...",
    "originalName": "photo.jpg",
    "storageType": "local",
    "mimeType": "image/jpeg",
    "path": "src/uploads/images/1749200000.jpg",
    "createdAt": "...",
    "updatedAt": "..."
}
```

---

