# Postman Collection Summary

| Method | Endpoint                 | Description                     |
| ------ | ------------------------ | ------------------------------- |
| POST   | `/api/upload/local`      | Upload file to local storage    |
| POST   | `/api/upload/cloudinary` | Upload file to Cloudinary       |
| POST   | `/api/upload/database`   | Upload image to MongoDB         |
| GET    | `/api/files`             | Get all uploaded files          |
| GET    | `/api/files/:id`         | Get single file metadata        |
| GET    | `/api/image/:id`         | Display image stored in MongoDB |
| DELETE | `/api/files/:id`         | Delete file record              |

