# Testing Order (Recommended)

Follow this sequence during your demo:

```
1️⃣ POST  /api/upload/local

↓

2️⃣ GET   /api/files

↓

3️⃣ GET   /api/files/:id

↓

4️⃣ POST  /api/upload/cloudinary

↓

5️⃣ POST  /api/upload/database

↓

6️⃣ GET   /api/image/:id

↓

7️⃣ DELETE /api/files/:id
```

This order demonstrates every feature required by the mentor's task: local storage, Cloudinary storage, MongoDB image storage, metadata retrieval, image display, and deletion.
